#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""edge-sources — Unified external source search.

Usage:
    edge-sources "topic"                          # default intent: research
    edge-sources "topic" --intent planner         # routing by intent
    edge-sources "topic" --sources x,hn,arxiv     # override source selection
    edge-sources --front-page                     # headlines only (for heartbeat)
    edge-sources "topic" --json                   # JSON output

Runs all sources concurrently, curates by signal, outputs structured markdown.
Claude WebSearch is treated as a managed fallback path, not a direct source
bypass. WebFetch remains the read path for URLs returned by sources.
"""

